            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Context matters. DR 40-50 is competitive for local businesses, DR 60+ is strong across most industries, DR 80+ is reserved for major brands. Benchmark against direct SERP competitors instead of universal targets.</p></div></div>
          </div>
